## Partie deux

plan d'adressage :

u     users       10.3.10.0      vlan 10
a     admin       10.3.20.0      vlan 20
s     stagiaire   10.3.30.0      vlan 30
srv   server      10.3.40.0      vlan 40
p     printers    10.3.50.0      vlan 50

MODE ACCESS :
conf t
interface ethernet 
switchport mode access
switchport access vlan
